ENTRY       EC 4.2.3.138                Enzyme
NAME        (+)-epi-alpha-bisabolol synthase
CLASS       Lyases;
            Carbon-oxygen lyases;
            Acting on phosphates
SYSNAME     (2E,6E)-farnesyl-diphosphate diphosphate-lyase (cyclizing, (+)-epi-alpha-bisabolol-forming)
REACTION    (2E,6E)-farnesyl diphosphate + H2O = (+)-epi-alpha-bisabolol + diphosphate [RN:R10274]
ALL_REAC    R10274
SUBSTRATE   (2E,6E)-farnesyl diphosphate [CPD:C00448];
